{"tid":202014,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"台超市總裁「劉鳴煒上身」　批年輕人很會花錢　籲勿計較人工低","createTime":"2017-04-15T07:40:28.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-15T17:20:54.000Z","uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"2447f8286ef1c65f7ad80165e2c10165171d9d8e","tid":202014,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T07:40:28.000Z","msg":"全聯總裁徐重仁稱「現在台灣的年輕人很會花錢，你到國際機場看，很多年輕人出國，很少看到老一輩的人。」（中央社）<br />\n「去少啲日本」燒到去台灣？台灣打工仔低薪問題延續多年，「大學畢業月薪22K」（2.2萬元新台幣，即約5,600港元，泛指大學畢業生人工低）現象一直都是社會問題。不過，有公司總裁反過來，批評年輕人「很會花錢」。<br />\n<br />\n稱很多年輕人去旅行　又要買最新手機<br />\n<br />\n全聯福利中心是台灣一間主打廉價貨品的超級市場，《自由時報》報道，總裁徐重仁在新書發布會上，稱「現在台灣的年輕人很會花錢，你到國際機場看，很多年輕人出國，很少看到老一輩的人。」認為年輕人要自己「能力範圍內」的事，社會誘惑很多，大家都想買最新的手機、最新的設備，每個人都想花更多的錢，但如果現在沒有那麼多的錢，就應該少花一點。"},{"pid":"8517329bf7e32917cea5c489cda37c1b1fdeaab2","tid":202014,"uid":39800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T07:42:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f8bcc145a1f19992f3bfc99bbf585a7fe0a8fdb","tid":202014,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T07:42:59.000Z","msg":"台仔五千零蚊個月買iphone又真係幾串"},{"pid":"ea0c90e62fafafa915411de62c24b320a1d8ad3c","tid":202014,"uid":37733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T07:43:51.000Z","msg":"證明劉鳴煒講得岩"},{"pid":"efb90838e1dae0af1f1137da2f791ffe715496c3","tid":202014,"uid":72009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T07:45:00.000Z","msg":"又一班連登仔支持商家佬<br />\n年輕人享樂是罪<br />\n不停為他們工作才是好青年"},{"pid":"665137c077601d6e915f5f94425664d7d855c975","tid":202014,"uid":9887,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T07:45:45.000Z","msg":"佢比人屌到收晒皮要道歉啦<br />\n你睇大瘤<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2febfbb0a7de37692d99fea204946f089b002c8c","tid":202014,"uid":72009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T07:46:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>證明劉鳴煒講得岩</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n年輕人要學佢後母咁上進"},{"pid":"7118c189b85447594e0a912363f545d493e11c9d","tid":202014,"uid":4783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T07:52:04.000Z","msg":"如果班後生好似日本咁唔撚洗錢你估佢份工仲有無得撈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"05c4471b6034ab16fcc257b9451c85d16312cdc7","tid":202014,"uid":72009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T07:53:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>佢比人屌到收晒皮要道歉啦<br />\n你睇大瘤<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n香港相反，特別是連登仔。"},{"pid":"27229def395a92b5a8318e1d5ad8b00178b2d9c2","tid":202014,"uid":106259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T10:39:36.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ffaf99db6817bf08277e94c866aa5bb6e3e1fbda","tid":202014,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T11:22:29.000Z","msg":"@腦魔"},{"pid":"db2d28b843829185b5525541fc2a1f9c3419db5b","tid":202014,"uid":51720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T12:29:58.000Z","msg":"首先你要家底鴻厚（具有財富繼承）先至做到 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n大學畢業，竟要做長工時、重度體力勞動、最低時薪兼無額外福利嘅工種，<br />\n值得可憐 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df093be02501ea577e8edc3f696d2b8b28588f31","tid":202014,"uid":106259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T17:20:54.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}